{"tid":1551123,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"《願榮光》作者 有重要澄清阿!!! (update repost)","createTime":"2019-09-08T00:15:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T00:46:05.000Z","uid":97826,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8e05e0480c71a11835f3c85d946b2522a7064532","tid":1551123,"uid":97826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:15:11.000Z","msg":"Q1. 唱歌就係左膠 唔唱得歌!!!<br />\nA1: 自古以黎 軍隊有軍歌 民族有佢地傳統歌<br />\n唔係上戰場時唱 (因為太嘈) 而係平時用黎凝聚人心 增加士氣<br />\n(google do soldiers sing)<br />\n&quot;Outside of combat, singing together in the military is fairly common though, as cheesy as it sounds. It passes time and boosts moral in shitty conditions.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nQ2: 國咩歌?!<br />\nA2: 由始至終都係抗爭者進行曲,  國歌唔係 你話係就係, 亦唔係你話唔係就唔係,<br />\n呢個係民主討論結果<br />\n而且都冇國 國咩歌   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ3: 首歌好難聽 唔夠激<br />\nA3: 首先 激有2種   一種係旋律上  另一種係唱法<br />\n第1種較為主觀  俾大家聽返下樂器bgm ver   我自己覺得係夠激 而唔會太露骨  從壓抑到後面激昂都帶住莊嚴感   <br />\n第2種就比較少爭議    mv合唱版我地臨時錄 所以唱法冇可能係choir果種共鳴腔 <br />\n大部份係pop+用力少少既唱法<br />\n好多人講俄佬果首好激 因為除左旋律之外佢地唱法係呢隻,   如果用返pop唱法一樣會唔夠激<br />\n所以睇唱法之外仲要睇旋律<br />\n純樂器原版:<br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/dgx-dgx/anthem-ver30-by-dgx-yhl-t\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fdgx-dgx%2Fanthem-ver30-by-dgx-yhl-t&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=c4a5f560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/dgx-dgx/anthem-ver30-by-dgx-yhl-t</a>  <br />\nmv版:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=907cfaa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ4: 好多宣傳 又派紙仔 逼人唱有冇搞錯<br />\nA4: 唔應該逼人唱   <br />\n冇可能全部人都鐘意首歌    咁你地就搵另一首   OR覺得唔應該唱既就唔唱<br />\n<br />\n有追開POST既知道我地公開左既第1個星期係推極都推唔郁d post<br />\n但等多d人知道之後就完全唔洗推 好多人自發幫忙<br />\n<br />\n日程表 活動post都好多人post同宣傳 咁係咪逼你要參加呢?<br />\n分別係日程表/活動係冇聲<br />\n唱歌係有聲會入到你耳  <br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山各自努力  互相尊重所有手足既權利<br />\n現場多人唔想唱就唔好唱<br />\n多人想唱你咪俾佢地唱下   之後換你地想唱果首or唔唱<br />\n<br />\nQ5: 首歌係咪另有企圖<br />\nA5: 平時見大家唱今天我 光輝歲月  果D就真係唔激啦  <br />\n所以想幫大家加BUFF       錢我地團隊一蚊都未收過<br />\n成品仲可以免費下載        <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ6: 首歌而家點<br />\nA6: 我地錄左樂團版 執緊返d tracks同人聲拍子拉返準  editing上要大量功夫所以仲未出到<br />\n另外有2隊交響樂團係已錄/準備錄佢地versions  有專業choir<br />\n所以真心希望大家期待既激昂版可以盡快面世<br />\n英文版好多人寫  但仲未有最終決定 等大家再brainstorm下之後砌返一首出黎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/oadlF3E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FoadlF3E&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=e21c53eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://imgur.com/oadlF3E</a>"},{"pid":"420861973bff0f6b0a10c52826377b3be4687eb3","tid":1551123,"uid":97826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:15:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgur.com/oadlF3E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FoadlF3E&h=fb193e58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e185dc86cfb55addbd95a5fedaa1e6af49411885","tid":1551123,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:15:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89285f0f16389192fe839444172a1fd410c891c0","tid":1551123,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:17:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/89ZtTtG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F89ZtTtG.jpg&h=eb82e59e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"871b228511298a823b669f91988146f8010b8bff","tid":1551123,"uid":197691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:17:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6acc0b6c87a300ce84f178546eda417634eed471","tid":1551123,"uid":97826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08